{"tid":230244,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"這座城只有一個妳","createTime":"2017-05-05T08:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T08:29:38.000Z","uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f1716931b5a1fad6cbba50080fb16ba3643d16","tid":230244,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"初夏的氣味，喚醒了沉睡多時的記憶。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉的街道，盛載著我們無數的回憶。<br />\n<br />\n斷了聯絡，卻斷不了回憶的牽絆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人來人往，與千百臉孔在人生路上相互擦肩而過。<br />\n<br />\n終究未忘，默默守候著於回憶彼岸唯一的一個妳。"},{"pid":"0ddcad0724ddac151d81c94db49c2081c4e2d1e0","tid":230244,"uid":55683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢幾句野又令我諗返起一個人"},{"pid":"4e66ef8d832db066b136348564dfdb9d501bdb3f","tid":230244,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢幾句野又令我諗返起一個人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}